content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 20.20 - Commercial food processing establishment

State Regulations

Commercial food processing establishment means any
facility other than a milk or filled milk plant, to which bulk fluid milk
products and bulk fluid cream products are disposed of that uses such receipts
as ingredients in food products and has no disposition of fluid milk products
or fluid cream products other than those received in consumer-type
packages. Notes
